** Description: **

A fully automated VBA script that automates a custom email reply message and downloading of attachments to specified local directory


** Instructions **

Simply hit ALT+F11 while in outlook, paste in the entire script, hit "Run" and you're done! Just remember to run the Macro anytime you restart and open Outlook.


** Version **

This has been tested on Outlook 2007 and have known to work on Outlook 2010.


